Package dataManagement

Class Data

  • java.lang.Object
    • dataManagement.Data

  • public class Data
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a data instance with all relevant information for the test runs. For each test run, a data instance is created by importing the information from a pre-defined Excel. The decision review and location planning model are applied on the data instance and define a optimal solution.
    Author:
    RamonaZauner
